title: That's Not How You Do It (English, Lunar Scans & The Blank)
description: 'Dohyun,' a former professional gamer trainee who was kicked out, is still the Internet Cafe's King today. But a single mistake causes a quarrel between him and the ill-tempered 'Hyuna'. But... If I win just one game, she'll take away my virginity? Sure... do it... then...
author: Yang Chong
